        YAAFI comes already with the following services since they are generally useful and
        do not add any dependencies

        <table>
          <tr>
            <th>Name</th>
            <th>Desciption</th>
          </tr>
          <tr>
            <td><a href="servicemanagerservice.html">ServiceManagerService</a></td>
